<li id="fn498" role="doc-endnote"><p>以有此三德也。——王弼<a href="#fnref498" class="footnote-back" role="doc-backlink">↩︎</a></p></li>
<li id="fn499" role="doc-endnote"><p>互卦，去掉初爻和六爻，中间四爻上三爻称为上互卦，下三爻称为下互卦。<a href="#fnref499" class="footnote-back" role="doc-backlink">↩︎</a></p></li>
<li id="fn500" role="doc-endnote"><p>查阅之后确认解卦读音为xiè，因为《易·杂卦传》里有：谢，缓也。即谢，通松懈的懈。<a href="#fnref500" class="footnote-back" role="doc-backlink">↩︎</a></p></li>
<li id="fn501" role="doc-endnote"><p>夙，早也。<a href="#fnref501" class="footnote-back" role="doc-backlink">↩︎</a></p></li>
<li id="fn502" role="doc-endnote"><p>田，猎也。<a href="#fnref502" class="footnote-back" role="doc-backlink">↩︎</a></p></li>
<li id="fn503" role="doc-endnote"><p>震为足也，此处拇指大脚趾。<a href="#fnref503" class="footnote-back" role="doc-backlink">↩︎</a></p></li>
<li id="fn504" role="doc-endnote"><p>维犹系也——闻一多。<a href="#fnref504" class="footnote-back" role="doc-backlink">↩︎</a></p></li>
<li id="fn505" role="doc-endnote"><p>sǔn，一种凶猛的鸟。<a href="#fnref505" class="footnote-back" role="doc-backlink">↩︎</a></p></li>
